     I                                        1  12 CHIN
     I                                        1   5 A5SHN1
     I                                        6  10 A5SHN2
     I                                       11  12 A5SHN3
      *------------*
      * START DATE *
      *------------*
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80SHIZK
     I                                        1   40SHZYY
     I                                        5   60SHZMM
     I                                        7   80SHZDD
      *----------*
      * END DATE *
      *----------*
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80EHIZK
